# Security Service — AtlasOS Agent Rules

- All authentication flows must use Keycloak/OIDC. No custom auth.
- All secrets must come from Vault via ESO. Never hardcode or use env files in production.
- All API endpoints must validate JWT tokens with proper scope/role checks.
- Audit logging is mandatory for all access control decisions.
- Encryption keys must rotate on schedule (90 days for data keys, 365 for master keys).
- Security scan (SAST + dependency audit) must pass before any merge.
